metadata.name: r00mz #1
metadata.description:
Get a r00m! and immerse yourself in an {Art}tificial Experimental Collection that merges the world of Ai-generated art and Web3, where pixel perfection is not the focus. 

This series presents 888 distinctive 1/1 collectibles that showcase the innovative potential of artificial intelligence in creating a diverse range of pixel art workstations. 

Created under Creative Commons (CC0) license, embracing a realm where no rights are reserved and creativity flows freely.
